Let us briefly comment on the physical meaning of the potential
. If we had inserted  the probe D3
branes (carrying the Wilson loops) at the edge of the deconstructed
region,  i.e. at , we would have had  massive - bosons in the theory and 
 would be  related to their interaction
potential. However in order to make the sources infinitely massive,
and hence to have the analogues of quarks in the fundamental
representation, we have to move the probe D3 branes and the
Wilson loop away to . Then the  parameter is 
modified by  i.e. 
